      <div class="comment_text_container">
      	<div class="comment_text">
	  	      		<p>Most of us do not have luxury of 8 hours of sleep. If we are lucky, we can have 6 hours of sleep at night. But the quality of your sleep is far more important than the number of hours you have slept. Even though you are crashing for only less than 8 hours, you should make sure that you are getting the most out of it. Get the right mattress. This can significantly improve your sleep. Many people now opt for semi-firm mattresses as a way to alleviate back pains and pressure points.</p>
    	  </div>
	      <p class="metadata"><a href="http://ririanproject.com/2007/06/21/how-to-sleep-more-effectively-starting-tonight/comment-page-2/#comment-202701" class="comment_date">May 2, 2010 at 7:06 pm</a><a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2007/06/21/how-to-sleep-more-effectively-starting-tonight/?replytocom=202701#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-202701", "202701", "respond", "169")'>Reply</a></p>
      </div>
</li>
   <li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-202727">
